<hw>law-makers</hw> <pos>n. pl.</pos> <def>Those persons who make or
amend or repeal laws, collectively.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> legislature, legislative assembly, general
assembly.</syn>⟦br⟧
